---
title: Cross-Feature Merge Queue
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant FA as Feature A
    participant FB as Feature B
    participant REG as Registry
    participant MQ as Merge Queue

    FA->>REG: register(claims=[db:schema:users, api:/auth/*])
    REG-->>FA: registered

    FB->>REG: register(claims=[db:schema:users, api:/profile/*])
    REG->>REG: analyze_conflicts → PARTIAL (db:schema:users overlap)
    REG-->>FB: registered (PARTIAL feasibility)

    Note over FA,MQ: Both features implement in parallel worktrees

    FA->>MQ: enqueue(priority=1)
    FB->>MQ: enqueue(priority=2)

    MQ->>MQ: pre_merge_checks(Feature A)
    MQ->>MQ: merge Feature A to main
    MQ->>REG: deregister(Feature A)

    MQ->>FB: rebase onto updated main
    FB-->>MQ: rebased
    MQ->>MQ: pre_merge_checks(Feature B)
    MQ->>MQ: merge Feature B to main
    MQ->>REG: deregister(Feature B)
